What would you like your website to be called? ACA
Which would you like to be the primary function of your website? A Forum
What topic would you like on your forum? Technologic news
Would it be free? Yes
How would the people sign in? With a username and mail
Would you like a news section? Yes
Who would write the news? A group of moderators, authorized people by the website
Would you like comments and likes in your website? Yes
Will the people be able to send pictures? Yes, Gifs, pictures and videos, as well as in the news section
Would any type of comment have any priority? No
Would you like that the website was divided by topics? Yes
What security feature would you like? A person will be able to post something every 90 seconds
Any extra feature? No
